sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant API
    participant MailRequestSvc
    participant MailRequestRepo
    participant Notifier
    participant Channel
    participant Provider
    participant EmailAPI
    participant NotificationLogRepo

    Admin->>API: Resolve mail request
    API->>MailRequestSvc: Transition ACTIVE -> RESOLVED
    MailRequestSvc->>MailRequestRepo: Persist lifecycle change

    MailRequestSvc->>Notifier: Trigger mail-arrived notification

    Notifier->>Channel: Build notification
    Channel->>Provider: Send via transport adapter
    Provider->>EmailAPI: POST /send [JSON/HTTPS]

    EmailAPI-->>Provider: 200 / Error
    Provider-->>Channel: Result
    Channel-->>Notifier: Result

    Notifier->>NotificationLogRepo: Persist attempt outcome
